            "name": "Monster Core pg. 86",
            "type": "link"
          },
          "name": "Monster Core",
          "page": 86,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "These shapeless masses of quivering flesh are the least of devilkind. Pathetic creatures from Hell's first layer, orts roam alongside damned and suffering souls. Nessaris can combine the essence of a mob of orts to concentrate their collective wickedness within a single form, granting it an infernal sentience and transforming it into a more powerful devil (see the nessari's Shape Devils ability).",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
